Ask
===

Created:      2012-11-28
Home page:    <https://metacpan.org/release/Ask>
Bug tracker:  <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=Ask>
Maintainer:   Toby Inkster <mailto:tobyink@cpan.org>

0.007  2013-06-18

 - (Addition) AskX::AutoLang.
 - (Bugfix Update) Bumped Moo version requirement to 1.000006.
   Fixes GH#1
   ++$JBERGER
 - Add a 'lang' option; use Lingua::Boolean::Tiny to process it.
   ++$DAXIM
 - Use POSIX.pm to switch off terminal echo instead of Term::ReadKey.
   ++$HAARG

0.006  2013-01-16

 - (Addition) XML address book example script.
 - (Documentation) Corrections in Ask::Wx pod.

0.005  2013-01-16

 - (Addition) Ask::Fallback backend, which kicks in if
   $ENV{AUTOMATED_TESTING} or $ENV{PERL_MM_USE_DEFAULT}.
 - (Addition) New (internal) API method: is_usable
 - (Addition) New (internal) API method: quality
 - Saner implementation of Ask->detect, using Module::Pluggable.

0.004  2013-01-14

 - (Addition) Ask::Wx - does not yet support multi file selection dialog.
 - (Addition) New API method: multiple_choice
 - (Addition) New API method: single_choice
 - (Bugfix) Correctly destroy no longer used Tk::MainWindow objects created
   in info, warning, question and file_selection methods.

0.003  2013-01-13

 - (Addition) Ask::Gtk

0.002  2012-12-11

 - (Packaging) Require at least version 0.006 of namespace::sweep.

0.001  2012-12-03  # Initial release

 - (Addition) Allow functions to be exported via
   Sub::Exporter::Progressive.
 - (Addition) Respect PERL_ASK_BACKEND environment variable.
 - (Documentation) Document Ask::Callback.
 - (Documentation) Document Ask::Tk.

0.000_02  2012-12-03  # Developer preview II

 - (Addition) Ask::Tk
 - (Packaging) Fix repo link.

0.000_01  2012-12-01  # Developer preview


